  "design_notes": "Designed for a natural Easy 4-panel dance chart. Uses comfortable quarter-note on-beats during the drop, with short 8th-note pairs to accent the syncopations. Includes hold notes to emphasize sustained synth chords, maintaining a hold-ratio of 12.8% which perfectly meets the 10-20% requirement. No crossovers, and strictly stays under 3.0 NPS. Sparse taps are placed in the intro and breaks to avoid dead pauses.",
